{"tid":1858384,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拒絕過太人多  而家有報應","createTime":"2020-02-02T16:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T15:50:33.000Z","uid":235006,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"68f8661f464d153104bc561f4b669b9ee2105bbd","tid":1858384,"uid":235006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:13:32.000Z","msg":"讀書既時候  從來都唔會為冇女而苦惱<br />\n有機打就得喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拍唔拍拖冇乜所謂<br />\n<br />\n由小學到中學  d女仔都好中意同我玩<br />\n話覺得我好搞笑  <br />\n有d當我係姊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細個對感情又真係有d遲頓，佢地要畫出腸我先知佢地既心意，最後俾我拒絕埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次拍拖係中學既時候，個女仔追左我兩個月，最後感動答應左。<br />\n不過冇錫過冇攬過，覺得拍拖唔應該做呢d野<br />\n最後唔夠兩個月佢就飛左我  同第二個一齊。。。<br />\n<br />\nA3 加埋都係拍得4個月左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾我開聲拒絕既冇數漏既話有6個<br />\n其他明示暗示無表示就唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家做緊工程 直頭女同事都冇個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抵我有今日啦  <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7dcdc51f241f7b9bf7689e478a450cde0bb9ac3","tid":1858384,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30f4cf9afa541b021cc1c48b301dccf24a9d46b","tid":1858384,"uid":86119,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:14:37.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"d6e417f97e32a1565d343eadc89145261703d6d8","tid":1858384,"uid":243175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:14:48.000Z"